            <h2>About LinkedIn Lead Generator</h2>
            <p>This tool helps you find and contact potential business leads by searching LinkedIn profiles and company websites.</p>
            
            <h3>Features:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Search LinkedIn profiles based on keywords, location, industry, and company size</li>
                <li>Extract contact information including email addresses and phone numbers</li>
                <li>Find company websites and social media profiles</li>
                <li>Export data to CSV or Excel formats</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>How to use:</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Enter search keywords (job titles, skills, etc.)</li>
                <li>Apply filters as needed (location, industry, company size)</li>
                <li>Click "Generate Leads" to start the search</li>
                <li>View results and export data as needed</li>
            </ol>
            
            <p><strong>Note:</strong> This tool respects LinkedIn's terms of service and rate limits. For best results, use specific keywords and filters.</p>
